Loving the contrast between the extreme technobabble / RAISA Footnotes and the delightfully wacky, kick-ass reality within this pocket dimension. It came on a bit heavy at first, but once I sunk my teeth into the logs, I was all in.

My only real crit is I can't get behind using blank log-lines to denote a period of silence. Elipses, (silence), or even pause, sure, but just an empty line? It does the job, but it still stands out a shade. There's also a few SPaG errors and redundancies  but this is a jam, so who's counting?

+1

P.S. I wrot a ting? I wrot a ting.





